results.deck: Mitchell corp, formerly an import/export company, converted its operations to home and arcade game development in the mid-1980s.
results.description:
A Japanese developer, the Mitchell Corporation was founded in 1960. When the company's ownership passed from father to son, Roy Ozaki steered the company in a new direction: the development of home and arcade video games.

Mitchell Corp. is best known for their Buster Bros and Puzz Loop series of games, as well as Osman.
